        <updateDate>2009-01-26T17:07:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Constitutional Amendment - Declares that the Constitution shall not be construed to prohibit individual or group prayer in public schools or other public institutions.</p> <p>Prohibits the United States or any state from requiring any person to participate in prayer or from prescribing the content of any prayer.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
